# Dev scoped verify (default agent gate)

Ordinary substantive edits → **dev scoped gate** before done summary. **Not** full **`yarn testbatch:verify`**.

Full gate ([testing-terminal-isolation.mdc](testing-terminal-isolation.mdc) **Full quality gate**) only when:

- [final-cleanup.mdc](final-cleanup.mdc) / [fantasia-final-cleanup](../skills/fantasia-final-cleanup/SKILL.md)
- User explicitly asks: **`yarn testbatch:verify`**, full verify, full gate, **`testbatch:ensure:*`**, or equivalent
- **`git commit`** ([git-conventional-commits.mdc](git-conventional-commits.mdc)) — changelog-only exception unchanged

CI / push still **`yarn testbatch:verify`** ([`.github/workflows/verify.yml`](../../.github/workflows/verify.yml)).

## Dev scoped gate (one terminal chain)

Playbook: [fantasia-dev-scoped-verify](../skills/fantasia-dev-scoped-verify/SKILL.md). Order:

1. **ESLint** — **`yarn eslint`** on touched compile paths (**`src/`**, **`src-electron/`**, **`types/`**, **`i18n/`**, **`helpers/`** non-Playwright, configs, **`.storybook-workspace/`**, tests). Expand to parent feature folder when SFC + colocated **`scripts/`** both edited.
2. **TypeScript** — **`yarn lint:typescript`** (full **`vue-tsc`**; cross-file breaks).
3. **Stylelint** — touched **`src/**/*.{vue,css,scss,sass}`** + **`.storybook-workspace/.storybook/**/*.{vue,css,scss,sass}`** only; skip when no style files touched.
4. **Connected Vitest** — **`yarn vitest run`** explicit **`*.vitest.test.ts`** paths from discovery; **no** **`yarn test:coverage:verify`**.

Stop on first failure; fix; re-run failed slice + connected specs on current tree.

**Escalate to full `yarn testbatch:verify`** (same turn) when batch touches: root **`eslint.config.mjs`**, **`vitest.config.mts`**, **`vitest/**`**, coverage thresholds, **`package.json`** deps/scripts affecting test/lint toolchain, or repo-wide refactor spanning many Vitest projects without obvious connected set.

## With dev compile smoke

After scoped gate passes → **20s** Electron compile smoke per [dev-electron-compile-check.mdc](dev-electron-compile-check.mdc) step 2 (separate terminal).

## Reporting

Done summary on substantive work: scoped gate **pass/fail** (which steps + spec paths) + dev compile **pass/fail**. Do not claim full verify green from scoped gate alone.

